    <completion-notes>
      FinancialCalculationToolHandler (540 LOC) for named formulas: simple_interest, compound_interest, present_value, future_value, loan_payment, ROI. All math in decimal (binding); double escape-hatch with quantize-back only for fractional/large-exponent compound interest. Exponent capped at 1000. Parameter validation surfaces parameter NAMES only (no values) per ADR-015. 30 unit tests pass: positive cases per formula + validation errors (negative inputs, unknown formula) + banker's rounding default + decimal precision determinism (0.1+0.2=0.3 exactly) + ADR-015 telemetry hygiene (sentinel scan). sprk_analysistool seed row in infra/dataverse/. Added entry to shared scripts/Seed-TypedHandlers.ps1. Build clean. BFF size delta: +0.04 MB. Quality gates pass.
    </completion-notes>
    <dependencies>100</dependencies>
    <blocks>105, 106, 107, 108, 109</blocks>
